# Last update stamps

The **prototypes hub** table reads each row’s date from that prototype’s source — keep those files in sync with real edits.

## Chatbot prototype (`ChatbotPrototype`, chat components)

Update **`src/app/lastUpdate.ts`**: set `CHATBOT_LAST_UPDATE_DISPLAY` to the current date/time (e.g. run `date '+%d %b %Y, %H:%M'` and paste). Commit with the change.

## Independent prototype (`prototypes/independent/`)

Update **`prototypes/independent/src/prototypeLastEdited.ts`**: set `INDEPENDENT_LAST_EDITED` when that standalone app changes meaningfully. Commit with the change.

Hub-only changes (copy/layout on `PrototypesHub` that are not a prototype edit) do not require bumping the other prototypes’ dates.
